java.lang.ClassNotFoundException: java.util.concurrent.CompletableFuture

The following of course works fine:

```
         Failsafe.with(retryPolicy).get(new Callable<Response>() {
                @Override
                public Response call() throws Exception {
                    ...
                }});    
```

